Notes on the Reddit corpus specifically:

The corpus consists of public Reddit posts and comments collected via the
official Reddit API. Usernames have not been retained. The corpus is
redistributed for research reproducibility under non-commercial fair-use
research-purpose conventions documented in Proferes et al. (2021) and
Fiesler et al. (2020). Users wishing to reproduce the corpus de novo can
do so using the scraper code provided in src/, subject to current Reddit
API terms and rate limits.

Should Reddit's terms of service change in a way that limits redistribution
of corpus data, this repository will be updated accordingly.
